<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>调查； 侦查；调查研究：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The police are investigating the robbery. 
警方正在调查这起抢劫案。</p></div>

